54
00:36:02.145 --> 00:36:03.228
Ok.

55
00:36:04.478 --> 00:36:05.603
D'accordo.

56
00:36:05.686 --> 00:36:07.478
Un momento, glielo passo.

57
00:36:37.645 --> 00:36:38.478
Grazie.

58
00:38:29.520 --> 00:38:31.270
